POtHS - Gospel Music - 11 - WoW Gospel - 1998 thru 2011

These are Someones picks for the 30 Best Gospel Songs for each year, 13 in all. The only problem with me is that they cover to many genre of Gospel Music. They try to cover to big of Music Area, rather than focusing on one area. I think they should at least have 3 divisions maybe more. Then we could pick better. 50% of these songs I would not purchase just cause it ain't in my favorites. A lot of the Newer Music is for younger people that I just prefer not to listen too. All in all there is some Gospel for everyone. (I know how my Dad felt now when Jimi Hendrix came out)
